metadata.name: Integrity
metadata.description:
This is 1 NFT in a collection of 13 masks that have been issued as a single, unique edition. 

Integrity Mask. 

Integrity is the foundation. The true state. It is when you interact with all the parts of your personality, become aware of them, give each of them a place within yourself, and allow each to manifest in this life when it is needed. 

From the state of wholeness comes love, acceptance, awareness, and wisdom.
